    "In addition to CNNs, ViTs have been successfully applied to medical image recognition and classification [14]; and a competitive alternative called multilayer perceptron (MLP)-Mixer has been proposed by Tolstikhin et al. [18] to perform image classification using exclusive MLPs without convolutions or attention blocks."
